    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>potatoes </strong>(skins on) into thin fries</p><p>Add the <strong>fries</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20-30 min or until they're cooked through and crisp</p>",
